Note: PASS METADATA
Note: ============================================================================

Process called "get_devirtualization_pass_name" returns Integer:
    Return proc create_from_literal from StringCore with "Devirtualization"
End Process

Process called "get_devirtualization_pass_description" returns Integer:
    Return proc create_from_literal from StringCore with "Resolves indirect calls to direct named calls via function-pointer dataflow analysis, with pointer-equality guarded speculation for partially resolved sites"
End Process
